longBusinessSummary: Encanto Potash Corp. engages in the exploration and mine development of potash properties in the province of Saskatchewan, Canada. Its flagship property is the Muskowekwan First Nation project covering an area of approximately 61,114 acres located to the north of Regina, Saskatchewan. The company was incorporated in 1986 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
